*hal-info-20070326 (30 Mar 2007)

  30 Mar 2007; Steev Klimaszewski <steev@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +hal-info-20070326.ebuild:
  New package, that holds all the fdi files for hal.  Works on my Dell, Sharp,
  (OLD) Thinkpad, and Efika, as well as my AMD64 machine, so only keyworded
  ~x86, ~ppc, and ~amd64.

